mqtt-monitor (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of MQTT Monitor.
  * Monitors disk SMART attributes, RAID status, and system metrics.
  * Publishes to MQTT for Home Assistant integration.
  * Supports automatic version updates via GitHub Releases.
  * Includes log rotation and configuration preservation.

